on-024.log\n1028\t\n1029\t## Iteration 25 — 2026-04-25T12:10:02Z — OK\n1030\t- **Log**: iteration-025.log\n1031\t\n1032\t## Iteration 26 — 2026-04-25\n1033\t\n1034\t- Iterations 21-25 all rate-limited at session start without producing\n1035\t  changes; the FR-6 query + component test files were already authored in\n1036\t  iteration 19/20's parallel work but had not been wired through the test\n1037\t  loop — and one assertion was failing because `u-1` appears twice in the\n1038\t  rendered DOM (header meta + identity `<dl>`).\n1039\t- Fixed `peek/src/components/__tests__/user-detail-view.test.tsx`'s\n1040\t  \"renders each section's data\" case:\n1041\t  - Replaced `screen.getByText(\"u-1\")` with\n1042\t    `getAllByText(\"u-1\").length >= 2` so the header user-id meta + the\n1043\t    identity-section `<dd>` both count as evidence of the populated\n1044\t    identity render.\n1045\t  - Replaced the bare `screen.getByText(\"3\")` (challenge total) with a\n1046\t    section-scoped `within(challengeSection).getByText(\"3\")` because `3`\n1047\t    can collide with retry counts / numeric values in other sections.\n1048\t  - Used `closest(\"section\")` from the `Challenges` `<h2>` to find the\n1049\t    DetailPanel section body without coupling to the section-id naming.\n1050\t- Net test surface for FR-6:\n1051\t  - `peek/src/server/db/queries/__tests__/get-peek-user-detail.test.ts`\n1052\t    — 16 tests: identity-only on miss; full-shape across every section;\n1053\t    suspicious-self-referral attention path; sparse fallbacks for every\n1054\t    aggregate; bounded recentLimit/tokenLimit binding; default limits;\n1055\t    payload-keyed event_queue lookup binds both userId + wallet; audit\n1056\t    handler invoked once with route+requestId on a successful read;\n1057\t    audit skipped when actorEmail missing / explicitly null / user not\n1058\t    found; thrown audit handler is swallowed; non-identity query\n1059\t    rejection propagates so the page can render a